Text: Thanks for the upload, but this is not a true eBook. This is made by scanning each page, it is not textual information.

Yeah sorry about that. It felt like the best way to categorize it at the time. I suppose it's not so adequate for blind people (with text reading programs) or people who want to copy and paste texts. I think it works okay though for other people who just want to read it.
Ebook is the perfect categorization for this upload. I've been curious about this, cheers for the share!
